cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.MA

The paper proposes a multi-objective reinforcement learning algorithm for bidding optimization in online real-time bidding. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves optimization and balancing of competing goals, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
